CHANGE
==================================================
- namelist_defaults_cam.xml
  Add ncdata path for IAPL35 and IAPL51

- cldwat2m_micro.F90
  Change iter from 2 to 4 to avoid 'Impossible case2 in instratus_condensate' error in cldwat2m_macro.F90 for IAPL35

- flexib.F90
  Add PHALFC51 and PHALFC35 for IAPL51 and IAPL35 
  Add Ndt, Ndq, DTDY to namelist for convenient test

- spmd_dyn.F90
  Add Ndt, Ndq, DTDY to namelist for convenient test

- stdatm.F90
  Change PBALIB and DPALIB from 0.5 to 0.25, which is used for IAPL51. For IAPL35 0.5 is OK.

==================================================
How to run IAPL35
==================================================

1) ./create_newcase -case iapl35 -res fd14_fd14 -compset FAMIPC5 -mach sugon_czy 

2) cd iapl35; vi env_conf.xml; Edit env_conf.xml as follows:
   <entry id="CAM_CONFIG_OPTS"   value="-phys cam5 -nlev 35 -v"  />

3) ./configure -case

4) ./iapl35.xxx.build

5) Edit atm namelist(atm_in) refering to the example file atm_in

  Need to be set manually:

&spmd_iap_inparm
 npr_yz         = 32,4,4,32
 DTDY           = 200.0D0  ! standard timestep for dynamics(for fast process)
 Ndt            = 3        ! 3x200=600s for slow process
 Ndq            = 3
/
  Automatically set:
  ncdata         = '/public/home/chzhy1/dat/inputdata/atm/cam/inic/IAP/IAPi_0000-01-01_128x256_L35_c180626.nc'

